                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the scribe; some letters in nomina sacra alternating with black letter (fols. 23rb, 24rb); incipit of Text I and its subsections; titles of the books to be read; one or two initial lines of prayers to be read; numbers of the prayers; directives to the ministers and their abbreviation (fol. 39vb); the word “amen” in fol.  24va; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals. &#xD;
